{"tid":1799773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立會議員默哀悼念周梓樂 張華峰離場","createTime":"2019-12-27T07:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T08:00:45.000Z","uid":42188,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3cd70de8c435387e85b53c9f5d9ad38c297493de","tid":1799773,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:56:04.000Z","msg":"周一（4日）凌晨將軍澳警民衝突期間，在尚德邨停車場墮樓重傷的科大學生周梓樂今早（8日）不治。立法會內會下午開會，公民黨郭榮鏗帶領在場議員及職員起立默哀3分鐘，<span style=\"color: red;\">原本在會議室的民建聯蔣麗芸和經民聯張華峰隨即離場</span>，會議室內建制派議員全部不在席。民主派議員並在卓面放上白花悼念周梓樂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5565cf730e89f0f818f3bd854edc9d474f26ba19","tid":1799773,"uid":53258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T07:59:23.000Z","msg":"民主派識玩就係會上悼念張個女, 睇下少數派離唔離場"},{"pid":"9051322fe8ca42fb00299b72bcf24b85d5140a35","tid":1799773,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:00:45.000Z","msg":"咁蔣麗芸..."}]}